cc:Work.dc:title: DECwriter Correspondent (LA12) Keyboard
cc:Work.dc:source: Redrawn from the 1983 Terminals and Printers Handbook, Figure 13-5
cc:Work.dc:description: Diagram of the DECwriter Correspondent keyboard. Corrections made from Figure 13-5 are: (1) Correct quote key to left of Return. (2) Margin labels are "Left/Top", "Right/Bottom" and "Recall/Store" and "Clear", per photograph. (3) Legend on SET UP key is "SET-UP".
